Package: tdata
Title: Prepare Your Time-Series Data for Further Analysis
Version: 0.2.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ramin", "Mojab", email = "rmojab63@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a set of tools for managing time-series data,
    with a particular emphasis on defining various frequency types such
    as daily and weekly. It also includes functionality for converting
    data between different frequencies.
